  "title": "ADMIN ASSISTANT",
  "description": "<h3>ADMIN ASSISTANT</h3><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><p><strong>Administrative Duties</strong></p><ul><li><p>Provide general administrative and clerical support to the office</p></li><li><p>Handle phone calls, emails, and correspondence</p></li><li><p>Maintain proper filing systems (physical and electronic)</p></li><li><p>Prepare reports, letters, and documents as required</p></li><li><p>Coordinate meetings, schedules, and appointments</p></li><li><p>Manage office supplies, pantry items, and service vendors</p></li></ul><p><strong>Purchasing / Procurement Duties</strong></p><ul><li><p>Assist in sourcing, requesting quotations, and comparing prices</p></li><li><p>Prepare and process Purchase Orders (POs) in a timely manner</p></li><li><p>Liaise with suppliers on orders, deliveries, and payment matters</p></li><li><p>Track purchase orders and ensure timely delivery of goods/services</p></li><li><p>Verify delivery orders and invoices for accuracy</p></li><li><p>Maintain proper purchasing records and supplier documentation</p></li><li><p>Support inventory tracking and stock control</p></li></ul>",
